strings: <voice_0x01001C72><se_high>Media princess: So far, our mission has been fulfilled <hero>.
<voice_0x01001C73><se_high>Media princess: Do you really believe that defeating Dolmagos will break the curse? Do you think everything will go back to normal?
<voice_0x01001C74><se_high>Media princess: I miss Trodin, I miss what it is.
<voice_0x01001C75><se_high>Media princess: We don't know where our journey will take us. but i will always be with you
<voice_0x01001C76><se_high>Media princess: You know I want to walk hand in hand in the royal garden like in the old days...
<voice_0x01001C77><se_high>Media princess: May all this be over soon...
